<div class="step-image">[[!img install/inc/infography/os-windows.png link="no" alt=""]]</div>

<p class="start">Start in Windows.</p>

[[!inline pages="install/inc/steps/install_intermediary_intro.inline" raw="yes" sort="age"]]

<div class="step-image">[[!img install/inc/infography/plug-first-usb.png link="no" alt=""]]</div>

1. Plug the first USB stick in the computer.

1. Click on the following link to download <span class="application">Universal USB Installer</span>:

   <a href='https://tails.boum.org/uui/Universal-USB-Installer.exe'>Download Universal USB Installer</a>

1. At the Windows security warning, confirm that you want to
run the program.

1. Read the license agreement and click <span class="button">I Agree</span>
to continue and start <span class="application">Universal USB Installer</span>.

   [[!img install/inc/screenshots/uui.png link="no" alt=""]]

1. Select <span class="guilabel">Tails</span> from the drop-down list.

   [[!img install/inc/screenshots/uui_tails.png link="no" alt=""]]

   <div class="step-image">[[!img install/inc/infography/install-intermediary-tails.png link="no" alt=""]]</div>

1. Click <span class="button">Browse</span> and choose the ISO image that you downloaded earlier.

1. Use the drop-down list to specify the USB stick on which you want to install
the ISO image.

   <div class="tip">
   <p>If the USB stick does not appear in the drop-down list, make sure
   that it is plugged in correctly and restart
   <span class="application">Universal USB Installer</span>.</p>
   </div>

1. Select the <span class="guilabel">Fat32 Format</span> option.

   [[!img install/inc/screenshots/uui_format.png link="no" alt=""]]

   <div class="caution">
   <p>If you forget to select the <span class="guilabel">Fat32
   Format</span> you will not be able to install the final Tails in step
   4.</p>

   [[!img install/inc/screenshots/uui_format.gif link="no" class="red-border" alt=""]]

   </div>

1. Click <span class="button">Create</span>.

1. A warning appears. Click <span class="button">Yes</span> to start the installation.
   The installation takes a few minutes.

1. After the installation is finished, click <span class="button">Close</span>
to quit <span class="application">Universal USB Installer</span>.

